	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你、<delay8 />你<tag a="110" b="0" />
你不是<tag a="110" b="4" />嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
