	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦咦！？<delay20 />
真的是你嗎？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />我很擔心你耶～<delay20 />
因為你甚至連道別都沒有，<delay20 />
就消失得無影無蹤了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請讓我正式地說……<delay frames="40" />
