	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～～<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x1" />個月來，你都跑到哪去啦？<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />
少了你這個開心果，<delay20 />
大家都覺得很寂寞喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="14" />但是從今天開始，<delay8 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />
