	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" />我是看到幻覺了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
已經消失的<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
