<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎回來──！<delay8 />你是什麼時候回來的？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />已經<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x1" />個月沒看見你，<delay20 />
我還以為<delay20 />你已經不會回來了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />停滯的時間再次開始流動，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />的景色<delay8 />
再次開始擁有生動的色彩，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<tag a="110" b="4" />！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎回來──！<delay8 />
你終於回到這裡了。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />你不在的這段時間，<delay20 />
我的心就好像<delay8 />
缺了一個大洞啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />
現在又能像這樣與你重逢，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是感謝上天的保佑啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗨，<tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay20 />
我們<delay8 />很久沒見面了呢，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概有<tag a="90" b="1" arg="0x1" />個月了吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="24" />如果你私底下其實有在<delay8 />
偷偷和其他人見面，<delay20 />
我可是會吃醋的喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />你只要偶爾像這樣來找我聊聊天，<delay20 />
我就很開心了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
