	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="16" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />
總算是輪到我了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的心就像是紫色的銀蓮花！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花語是<tag a="110" b="0" />「深信不疑的等待」喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="12" />你一直都不來找我，<delay20 />
